	* font/devps/BMI:
	* font/devps/BMR:
	* font/devps/CB:
	* font/devps/CBI:
	* font/devps/CI:
	* font/devps/CR:
	* font/devps/HB:
	* font/devps/HBI:
	* font/devps/HI:
	* font/devps/HNB:
	* font/devps/HNBI:
	* font/devps/HNI:
